{"tid":155242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人仲記得 包容 體諒 嗎？","createTime":"2017-03-14T00:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T02:18:16.000Z","uid":64259,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da6487d155a6ed822d651da1bf6fba0a513a764f","tid":155242,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"依家既人 大部分都經唔起時間考驗<br />\n原因係 唔識咩都包容同體諒<br />\n<br />\n得罪請句<br />\n有人係睇樣 有人睇錢<br />\n性格只係其次<br />\n<br />\n無錯 無外在又點會有內在？<br />\n相由心生<br />\n<br />\n可惜既係<br />\n過左外在 你又嫌人內在唔得<br />\n<br />\n一部新電話 都要你不斷摸索 學習先識用<br />\n感情事都一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日314 希望大家多d 包容 體諒身邊既人<br />\n特別係家人 無條件既付出<br />\n情人無條件既陪伴<br />\n朋友 無條件既關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6e5c1077a926d07090911f13b191e3f2de4039","tid":155242,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43767098845893b17087e546a0454c4019787612","tid":155242,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"而家講包容係左膠係道德撚係狗"},{"pid":"291e37f0dd022a81c4931da98eaa22a109dfc7d2","tid":155242,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家講包容係左膠係道德撚係狗</blockquote><br />\n食屎喇"},{"pid":"8beab7860bf58f94fb643c23bbe4489b38b39370","tid":155242,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家講包容係左膠係道德撚係狗</blockquote><br />\n食屎喇</blockquote><br />\n連登仔價值呀屌你"},{"pid":"26791205eebe9e59480830604358057f33c1eab3","tid":155242,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"用理解比較好<br />\n包容二字已經越聽越嘔心"}]}